181  public function getSQL($alias = "", $aliases = null) {
182  if ($alias !== "") {
183  $targetEntityTable = $alias;
184  $alias = "`" . $alias . "`";
185  } else {
186  $targetEntityTable = $this->targetEntityTable;
187  }
188  $jtAlias = uniqid ( $this->joinTable );
189  $table = $this->table;
190  if (is_array ( $aliases )) {
191  if (isset ( $aliases [$this->table] ))
192  $table = $aliases [$this->table];
193  }
194  return " INNER JOIN `" . $this->joinTable . "` `{$jtAlias}` on `" . $jtAlias . "`.`" . $this->myFkField . "`=`" . $table . "`.`" . $this->myPk . "`" . " INNER JOIN `" . $this->targetEntityTable . "` {$alias} on `" . $jtAlias . "`.`" . $this->fkField . "`=`" . $targetEntityTable . "`.`" . $this->pk . "`";
195  }

213  public function generateConcatSQL() {
214  $sql = $this->getConcatSQL ();
215  $where = "";
216  if (($size = sizeof ( $this->whereValues )) > 0) {
217  if ($size > 3) {
218  $res = array_fill ( 0, $size, "?" );
219  $res [0] = "SELECT ? as _id";
220  $where = $this->getParserConcatWhereInMask ( implode ( " UNION ALL SELECT ", $res ) );
221  } else {
222  $mask = $this->getParserConcatWhereMask ( " ?" );
223  $res = array_fill ( 0, $size, $mask );
224  $where = "WHERE " . implode ( " OR ", $res );
225  }
226  }
227  return str_replace ( "{condition}", $where, $sql );
228  }
